data.description: Attention Investors/ Owner Occupants come check out this spacious duplex that has enormous potential, featuring 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms in the upstairs unit and 4 bedrooms and 1 bathroom in the downstairs unit. The downstairs unit has been recently updated, while the upstairs unit has renovation work in progress but is not yet complete. The roof is just 5 years old, installed in 2018, ensuring durability and peace of mind.
